et/Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-Ki%E1%BA%BFn/T%C3%A1i-h%E1%BA%A1/poem-95n2BNFu6k_jk3NfxpJ9yw">Tái hạ - 塞下</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-Ki%E1%BA%BFn/author-xOkIiHqP9P6nrS8jJbgRNg">Thường Kiến</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/T%E1%BB%91ng-Kh%C3%BAc-Th%E1%BA%ADp-thi%E1%BA%BFu-ph%E1%BB%A7/poem-R4iaGG8DCqemexlSGFxz1g">Tống Khúc Thập thiếu phủ - 送麴十少府</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/Tr%C3%A2m-c%C3%BAc/poem-1t_0qqRe4AB9PgmYyYa1yg">Trâm cúc - 簪菊</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Tuy%E1%BB%87t-c%C3%BA-m%E1%BA%A1n-h%E1%BB%A9ng-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-q1J1x7j8pFm6LP5a5RPHHQ">Tuyệt cú mạn hứng kỳ 2 - 絕句漫興其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
